OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers will
OL,6,Fease away through this evening,
OL,7,Fallowing it to become dry and clear
OL,8,Facross the region overnight. Turning
OL,9,Fchilly under the clear skies with a
OL,10,Ffew mist and fog patches possible and
OL,11,Fa touch of frost in the countryside.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FAny mist or fog will quickly
OL,14,Fclear in the morning. Staying dry with
OL,15,Fsunny spells at first, but cloud
OL,16,Flikely increasing during the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
